_:b0__56736 <http://www.w3.org/ns/locn#geometry> "POLYGON((1.60 72.30,42.70 72.30,42.70 52.00,1.60 52.00,1.60 72.30))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/Location>.
