<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#d2966defa7a052544600f8e724e6c976>.
<#d2966defa7a052544600f8e724e6c976> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://resources.stockholm.se/data/ed5cb18b-ff08-469a-a5c8-91eeef9510dc>;
